# Football Stars - Agent Operating File (.ai)

## Purpose
This file is the single source of truth for AI/code agents working on this repository.
Every agent MUST read this file before making code changes.
Every agent MUST update this file in the same PR/commit whenever behavior, flow, data model, routes, or UX rules change.

