## Current App Behavior (Canonical)

### Onboarding
- Route: `/onboarding`
- Mandatory for new/invalid state.
- Team list is generated dynamically from `PLAYERS` teams (min 2 players per team).
- User must select a team to continue.

### Navigation / Tabs
- `/(tabs)/index` = „С„Щ„™
- `/(tabs)/management` = „†„Щ„Ф„Х„Ь „І„С„Х„¶„Ф (Unlocked at 21 players)
- `/(tabs)/squad` = „Ф„°„Т„Ь „©„Ь„Щ
- `/(tabs)/gallery` = „©„Ч„І„†„Щ„Э
- `/(tabs)/generate` = AI (prompt-based generation via Pollinations)

### Player Quiz Rules
- Wrong answer closes question immediately (250ms delay) and is NOT counted.
- Correct answer increments `correctAnswers` in `playerProgress`.
- Player unlock at 4 correct answers (`unlocked: true` in state).
- Each question index tracked in `answeredIndices` to prevent re-answering.
- Answers are reshuffled on every question view.

### Squad Rules
- Shows ALL players from the favorite team with locked/unlocked visual state.
- Unlocked = green glow border + вЬЕ badge; Locked = dark overlay + рЯФТ + X/4 progress.
- DEV_FLAGS.UNLOCK_21_PLAYERS_FOR_TESTS overrides unlock status (routes all checks through `getUnlockedPlayers()`).
- Stage B progress bar = total unlocked across ALL teams (not just favorite).
- Two header buttons: рЯФД „І„С„Х„¶„Ф (navigate to onboarding, no data loss) | рЯЧС „Р„Щ„§„Х„° (wipe all data + onboarding).

### Management (League Season v2)
- Route: `/(tabs)/management`
- 4-3-3 slot lineup with role constraints:
  - `gk` вЖТ Goalkeeper only
  - back line slots вЖТ Defender
  - mid/wing/st slots вЖТ Midfielder or Forward
- No duplicate player assignment across slots.
- `„І„С„Ґ „Ф„®„Ы„С „Р„Х„Ш„Х„Ю„Ш„Щ` auto-fills lineup by slot rules without duplicates.
- Double-leg round-robin league season (10 teams √Ч 9 rounds).
- Play progresses round by round (`„©„Ч„І „Ю„Ч„Ц„Х„®`).
- Every round simulates all fixtures, updates league table and user stats.
- Match result UI: visual modal (score + teams + coins earned).
- **Post-Match Bonus:** Chance to double match coins by answering a random football quiz question.
- **Championship:** If user finishes 1st place, show trophy popup + championship coins bonus (200).
- Season can be reset via `„Ґ„Х„†„Ф „Ч„У„©„Ф`.

### Monetization & Ads
- **Strategy:** No persistent banners. Interstitial ads (Modal) on value actions only.
- **Trigger:** Download, Set Wallpaper, Share image.
- **Component:** `components/InterstitialAdModal.tsx` вАФ countdown + ad simulation.

### AI Image Generation
- Route: `/(tabs)/generate`
- Hebrew/English prompt input.
- Multiple styles: Realistic, Anime, Cartoon, Neon, Oil Painting.
- Powered by Pollinations AI (FLUX model, 1024√Ч1792px).
- Actions: Download to gallery, Share, Set as wallpaper вАФ all trigger interstitial ad.

### Temporary QA Override (Development)
- File: `constants/featureFlags.ts`
- `UNLOCK_21_PLAYERS_FOR_TESTS: true` вЖТ `getUnlockedPlayers()` returns 40 role-priority players in `__DEV__`.
- `QA_UNLOCKED_PLAYERS_COUNT: 40` вЖТ controls exact count.
- Ignored in production (`__DEV__ === false`).

